                     <label>Bookplates:</label> The <locus from="Inner_back_cover"
                        to="Inner_back_cover">left doublure</locus>: <q xml:lang="en">Bibliotheca
                        Lindesiana</q> with pencilled shelfmark <q xml:lang="en">F/4</q>.<lb/> The
